    loopz 100
    loope 100
    
    ja      200
    jnbe    200

For 8087 opcodes, you must specify the WAIT or FWAIT prefix, as the
following example shows:

    fwait fadd st,st(3)       ; this line assembles
                              ; an fwait prefix

