                                 \bMKDIR (MD)\p

Creates a directory.

You can use the MKDIR or MD command to create a multilevel directory
structure.

\bSyntax\p

    MKDIR [drive:]path

    MD [drive:]path

\bParameters\p

drive:
    Specifies the drive on which you want to create the new directory.

path
